author: The Associated Press
title: Israel's Benjamin Netanyahu to go into quarantine after aide tests positive
description: Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu's office says he will enter self-quarantine after an aide tested positive for coronavirus.
content:
Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu's office says he will enter self-quarantine after an aide tested positive for coronavirus.
